    </teiHeader> <text type="card"> <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs=""/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb150" type="place"><hi rend="pre-print">Wien, XVIII. Sternwartestrasse 71</hi></rs></addrLine></address><address><addrLine><pb facs=""/>Herrn Robert Adam</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb62" type="place">Wien XII/1</rs>.</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb1239" type="place">Meidlinger Hptstr 56</rs>.</addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><seg rend="left"><pb facs=""/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><date>8/1. 911</date>.</seg></dateline><p><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb150" type="place">Wien XVIII. Sternwartestrasse 71</rs></hi></p><salute rend="center">Sehr geehrter Herr,</salute></opener><p>nun hab ich Ihren <rs ref="#pmb33580" type="work">Neidhard</rs> (<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr intere<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>irt) ausgele<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en – we<c rendition="#gemination-n"/> es Ihnen geht, würd ich Sie im Laufe die<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>er Woche um Ihren freundl Be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>uch bitten; da ich, nach einer Influenza, <pb facs=""/>noch ganz hei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>er, er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <gap quantity="5" reason="illegible" unit="chars"/> hilfts;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>agen wir <date>Freitag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Abend</time> etwa <time>6 Uhr</time>?</p><closer>mit verbindll Grüßen<lb/>Ihr ergebn<unclear>er</unclear><lb/><signed>ArthSchnitzler</signed></closer></div></body> </text></TEI>